Description:Stormchaser's Talent enters battlefield pre-levelled at 2 (Counters:LEVEL=2). Activating the Level 3 ability ({5}{U}) advances the Class to level 3, installing the ongoing SpellCast trigger. Casting Lightning Bolt (an instant) then fires that trigger, creating a 1/1 blue/red Otter creature token with prowess. This confirms the L3 ongoing trigger works correctly (mtg-881 wave4).

